article_title: Vehicle and motorcycle involved in serious crash in Neptune
article_text:
Buy Photo A vehicle collided with a motorcycle about 9 p.m. Friday at Route 33 and Memorial Drive, said Sgt. Steve Colombo. (Photo: FILE)Buy Photo

NEPTUNE — A vehicle collided with a motorcycle about 9 p.m. Friday at Route 33 and Memorial Drive, said Sgt. Steve Colombo.

Colombo categorized the accident as "serious'' but said there were no fatalities reported.

He could not say whether victims were taken to hospitals.

Colombo said the accident is still under investigation and he was not authorized to release any details.
